# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:8
translate spanish u19a1s7_ffe8710d:

    # "At some point later I am woken by a noise coming from outside."
    "Más tarde, me despierta un ruido que viene de fuera."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:9
translate spanish u19a1s7_90e13adf:

    # "I listen and make out two voices speaking."
    "Escucho y distingo dos voces hablando."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:12
translate spanish u19a1s7_53f3a3ff:

    # dad "Must you do this in the middle of the night?"
    dad "¿Tienes que hacer esto en mitad de la noche?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:13
translate spanish u19a1s7_0fc0d617:

    # "Gruff Woman" "There is a rumor in the village that a man has come to town."
    "Gruff Woman" "Corre el rumor en el pueblo de que ha llegado un hombre a la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:14
translate spanish u19a1s7_3aafbf86:

    # "Gruff Woman" "That you are housing him here and that he has not submitted his tribute."
    "Gruff Woman" "Que lo estás alojando aquí y que no ha entregado su tributo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:15
translate spanish u19a1s7_6afb31e5:

    # "Gruff Woman" "The queen demands her tribute."
    "Gruff Woman" "La reina exige su tributo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:18
translate spanish u19a1s7_05ab2784:

    # "I lean over and peer out the window."
    "Me inclino y miro por la ventana."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:19
translate spanish u19a1s7_3627b9fd:

    # "There's a woman with greenish skin standing with two other armored guards in front of the house, talking with Dad."
    "Hay una mujer de piel verdosa de pie con otros dos guardias con armadura delante de la casa, hablando con papá."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:20
translate spanish u19a1s7_a4f99730:

    # dad "He is but a boy passing through. He'll be gone tomorrow."
    dad "No es más que un chico de paso. Mañana se habrá ido."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:21
translate spanish u19a1s7_5250d292:

    # dad "I'll gladly submit a tribute for him in the morning."
    dad "Con mucho gusto entregaré un tributo por él por la mañana."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:22
translate spanish u19a1s7_2380958a:

    # "Gruff Woman" "That's not good enough. I want to see this boy."
    "Gruff Woman" "Eso no es suficiente. Quiero ver a este chico."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:23
translate spanish u19a1s7_44510786:

    # "Gruff Woman" "Who is he? Where did he come from?"
    "Gruff Woman" "¿Quién es? ¿De dónde viene?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:26
translate spanish u19a1s7_92f1c337:

    # "Just then one of the guards holds up his lantern and looks right at me."
    "Justo entonces, uno de los guardias levanta su linterna y me mira directamente."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:27
translate spanish u19a1s7_04aea5fd:

    # "Guard" "Ma'am, there's somebody over there."
    "Guard" "Señora, hay alguien ahí."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:30
translate spanish u19a1s7_d2abee33:

    # "I quickly back away from the window. The room is so small though, there's nowhere to hide."
    "Rápidamente me alejo de la ventana. Pero la habitación es tan pequeña que no hay dónde esconderse."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:31
translate spanish u19a1s7_565c8ed8:

    # "And it doesn't take long before there's a knock on the door."
    "Y no tarda mucho en que llamen a la puerta."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:32
translate spanish u19a1s7_01d286ae:

    # "Gruff Woman" "You in there. Open up."
    "Gruff Woman" "Tú, la de ahí dentro. Abre."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:33
translate spanish u19a1s7_6c62e06b:

    # "Gruff Woman" "Or don't. I'm coming in, either way."
    "Gruff Woman" "O no lo hagas. Voy a entrar de todas formas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:36
translate spanish u19a1s7_2eb5a274:

    # "When the door opens, I see the woman who had been talking."
    "Cuando se abre la puerta, veo a la mujer que había estado hablando."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:37
translate spanish u19a1s7_220574ff:

    # "It takes me a moment to realize that it's Tammy, but once I see it, it's obvious."
    "Tardo un momento en darme cuenta de que es Tammy, pero una vez que la veo, es obvio."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:38
translate spanish u19a1s7_8e1f8e77:

    # "It's her, but she's an orc or something. More muscled, green skin, and little tusks sticking up from her bottom jaw."
    "Es ella, pero es una orca o algo así. Más musculosa, con la piel verde y unos pequeños colmillos que le sobresalen de la mandíbula inferior."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:41
translate spanish u19a1s7_65721986:

    # tm "This is no mere boy. This is every bit of a man."
    tm "Esto no es un simple chico. Es un hombre en toda regla."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:42
translate spanish u19a1s7_b7326379:

    # tm "Who are you? Where are you from?"
    tm "¿Quién eres? ¿De dónde vienes?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:43
translate spanish u19a1s7_d3287579:

    # pc "Uh… my name is [pcname]. I'm from Skyhill."
    pc "Eh… me llamo [pcname]. Soy de Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:44
translate spanish u19a1s7_bb8008e3:

    # tm "Nonsense. There are no settlements on Sky Hill."
    tm "Tonterías. No hay asentamientos en Sky Hill."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:47
translate spanish u19a1s7_8b480619:

    # tm "You should know that every person in Whiterock must make a tribute to the queen. She demands it."
    tm "Deberías saber que toda persona en Whiterock debe rendir tributo a la reina. Ella lo exige."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:48
translate spanish u19a1s7_b84d8598:

    # pc "I'm just here for the night. I'm leaving tomorrow."
    pc "Solo estoy aquí para pasar la noche. Me voy mañana."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:49
translate spanish u19a1s7_93788c82:

    # tm "Even one who is merely passing through must make their tribute."
    tm "Incluso quien está de paso debe rendir su tributo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:50
translate spanish u19a1s7_d2bb68ce:

    # pc "I have nothing to give."
    pc "No tengo nada que dar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:53
translate spanish u19a1s7_c700d1fa:

    # tm "Oh I don't know, it looks like you could give a lot."
    tm "Oh, no sé, parece que podrías dar mucho."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:56
translate spanish u19a1s7_28b7f8d3:

    # tm "Oh, interesting."
    tm "Oh, interesante."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:57
translate spanish u19a1s7_9e40dac7:

    # tm "That bracelet. It looks nice. That will do."
    tm "Esa pulsera. Es bonita. Servirá."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:58
translate spanish u19a1s7_1cd753fa:

    # tm "Hand it over. The queen will love it."
    tm "Dámela. A la reina le encantará."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:61
translate spanish u19a1s7_98dfd533:

    # pc "No! I need this."
    pc "¡No! La necesito."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:62
translate spanish u19a1s7_fc330265:

    # tm "Your desire for it makes it even more valuable to her."
    tm "Tu deseo por ella la hace aún más valiosa para ella."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:63
translate spanish u19a1s7_cb3ada8c:

    # pc "She can't have it!"
    pc "¡No puede quedársela!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:64
translate spanish u19a1s7_782dc006:

    # tm "I am taking that bracelet, one way or another."
    tm "Me voy a llevar esa pulsera, de una forma u otra."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:65
translate spanish u19a1s7_858ca7d7:

    # tm "It would be better if you do not fight me on this."
    tm "Sería mejor que no te opusieras a mí en esto."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:68
translate spanish u19a1s7_deab7719:

    # "I look for a way out of this. I can't run - they're blocking the door."
    "Busco una forma de salir de esto. No puedo correr: están bloqueando la puerta."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:69
translate spanish u19a1s7_d394c6cf:

    # "I could fight, but I'm naked while they are armed and armored and there's three of them."
    "Podría luchar, pero estoy desnudo mientras que ellos van armados y con armadura, y son tres."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:70
translate spanish u19a1s7_25912e1b:

    # "But I can't just give it to her either. Without the bracelet, I can't get back to my world."
    "Pero tampoco puedo simplemente dársela. Sin la pulsera, no puedo volver a mi mundo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:73
translate spanish u19a1s7_ee4c5d58:

    # "So I do the only thing I can think of and try to push my way out of the room."
    "Así que hago lo único que se me ocurre e intento abrirme paso para salir de la habitación."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:74
translate spanish u19a1s7_336e5378:

    # "But Tammy is solid and unmoving."
    "Pero Tammy es firme e inamovible."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:78
translate spanish u19a1s7_a309fb65:

    # "And her punch hits me like a baseball bat."
    "Y su puñetazo me golpea como un bate de béisbol."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:79
translate spanish u19a1s7_19b0e7cd:

    # "I can't help but stop in my tracks, hunch over, coughing. I feel like I'm going to throw up."
    "No puedo evitar detenerme en seco, encorvarme y toser. Siento que voy a vomitar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:82
translate spanish u19a1s7_7635aa02:

    # "When the second punch hits me in the back of the head..."
    "Cuando el segundo puñetazo me golpea en la nuca..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene7.rpy:87
translate spanish u19a1s7_69d06fb5:

    # "...I'm out like a light."
    "...me quedo inconsciente."

